WEBVTT

00:20.230 --> 00:21.290
This is exactly it.

00:21.600 --> 00:23.030
This is Huotu water.

00:23.160 --> 00:24.830
It was indeed formulated not long ago.

00:24.830 --> 00:27.160
But this amount
is just enough for one day.

00:27.230 --> 00:29.230
Where did you find this?

00:29.710 --> 00:32.439
If you can guarantee this
for 7 consecutive days,

00:32.520 --> 00:34.840
her eyes will be saved.

00:38.390 --> 00:40.560
I found it by accident.

00:41.600 --> 00:43.000
It's just a 7-day supply.

00:44.030 --> 00:45.490
What's so hard about that?

00:59.490 --> 01:00.020
Qiao,

01:00.470 --> 01:01.070
look up.

01:22.870 --> 01:24.880
Qiao, how do you feel?

01:34.229 --> 01:34.840
Li Ce.

01:36.000 --> 01:37.130
This is Huotu water.

01:38.070 --> 01:40.060
Zhuge Yue. It was sent by Zhuge Yue.

01:40.310 --> 01:41.000
Wait.

01:41.500 --> 01:43.479
This medicine is indeed Huotu water.

01:43.479 --> 01:43.950
But why must you assume

01:43.950 --> 01:45.550
that it was sent by Zhuge Yue?

01:45.789 --> 01:47.460
Couldn't it be me, the peerless,

01:47.460 --> 01:49.060
romantic, and elegant young man,

01:49.060 --> 01:50.410
who found it?

01:54.120 --> 01:56.310
I used this medicine
when I was in Qingshan Manor.

01:56.310 --> 01:58.229
It was formulated by the Zhuge family.

01:58.229 --> 01:59.789
After putting it in the eyes,

01:59.789 --> 02:01.480
you can see the smallest details

02:01.480 --> 02:03.510
and see in darkness
as clearly as in daylight.

02:03.510 --> 02:05.440
The person who sent me the medicine

02:05.580 --> 02:06.890
is Zhuge Yue, right?

02:07.230 --> 02:07.870
Qiao,

02:08.169 --> 02:08.949
this medicine...

02:08.949 --> 02:09.820
Last night,

02:10.360 --> 02:11.620
did you come to my room?

02:12.120 --> 02:13.580
Why would I go to your room?

02:15.750 --> 02:17.280
It wasn't you, as expected.

02:17.960 --> 02:18.750
It was him.

02:19.800 --> 02:21.000
It must have been him.

03:49.829 --> 03:54.960
[REBIRTH]

03:55.350 --> 03:58.000
[Episode 5]

04:17.360 --> 04:18.390
I knew it was you.

04:20.190 --> 04:21.430
General Zhuge.

04:28.240 --> 04:30.270
Your martial skill and intellect

04:30.390 --> 04:32.220
truly live up to your reputation.

04:32.220 --> 04:34.550
Everyone knows
you led the Moon Guard of 20

04:34.550 --> 04:36.350
and dared to sneak into Great Yan

04:36.480 --> 04:39.320
to fight Heir Apparent Yant's
massive Black Eagle Army.

04:39.320 --> 04:40.260
But they don't know after you fell into

04:40.260 --> 04:42.700
the extremely cold frozen lake
bordering Ximeng

04:42.700 --> 04:45.360
and have been searched for
by the Yan Army for 3 months,

04:45.360 --> 04:47.220
you actually managed to survive.

04:56.520 --> 04:57.920
Why are you here?

04:59.480 --> 05:00.800
Don't be so cold.

05:01.750 --> 05:03.150
I just don't understand,

05:03.630 --> 05:05.760
so I wanted to ask you on Qiao's behalf.

05:06.040 --> 05:07.190
Since you're not dead,

05:07.190 --> 05:08.670
why do you hide

05:09.120 --> 05:11.050
and refuse to show yourself to her?

05:15.360 --> 05:16.630
I have my own reasons.

05:17.430 --> 05:18.690
You don't need to know.

05:22.910 --> 05:23.830
General Zhuge.

05:28.920 --> 05:30.400
You are a grown man,

05:30.450 --> 05:31.850
yet so indecisive.

05:32.150 --> 05:33.510
If you want to reunite with her,

05:33.510 --> 05:34.440
just go up to her.

05:34.870 --> 05:36.600
She is waiting for you right now.

05:36.600 --> 05:38.860
If you still want to pretend you are dead,

05:39.040 --> 05:40.570
then stop sneaking around,

05:40.750 --> 05:42.080
visiting her one moment

05:42.120 --> 05:43.850
and sending medicine the next.

05:44.040 --> 05:45.100
Qiao is not stupid.

05:45.680 --> 05:48.080
How could she not sense
you're still alive?

05:54.510 --> 05:55.570
What are you doing?

05:55.750 --> 05:56.800
Am I wrong?

05:57.000 --> 05:57.680
Zhuge Yue.

05:58.480 --> 05:59.810
Are you going to kill me?

06:00.290 --> 06:01.040
Zhuge Yue.

06:01.680 --> 06:03.010
What are you going to do?

06:09.630 --> 06:10.600
Let me tell you,

06:11.160 --> 06:12.120
if you kill me,

06:12.200 --> 06:14.400
the consequences will be very serious.

06:26.510 --> 06:26.950
Qiao.

06:28.560 --> 06:29.620
Where is Zhuge Yue?

06:30.750 --> 06:31.480
Where is he?

06:32.000 --> 06:32.830
Zhuge Yue?

06:33.830 --> 06:34.690
He didn't come.

06:38.190 --> 06:39.510
Qiao, I told you

06:39.870 --> 06:41.900
that I asked Song Cheng
to find this medicine for you.

06:41.900 --> 06:43.300
Why don't you believe me?

07:09.390 --> 07:10.360
I know it's you,

07:11.240 --> 07:12.070
Zhuge Yue.

07:19.120 --> 07:19.800
Qiao,

07:21.240 --> 07:22.570
I want you to get better.

07:27.680 --> 07:28.480
Zhuge Yue,

07:29.360 --> 07:31.090
I will definitely wait for you.

07:47.360 --> 07:48.830
It's the 6th day now.

07:49.560 --> 07:50.190
Qiao,

07:50.600 --> 07:51.730
how are you feeling?

07:53.070 --> 07:54.800
I can vaguely see some light and shadows.

07:54.800 --> 07:55.630
That's great!

07:57.870 --> 07:59.000
These past few days,

07:59.120 --> 08:00.000
not only did I have Song Cheng

08:00.000 --> 08:01.560
find Huotu water for you,

08:02.310 --> 08:03.000
but I also had him bring

08:03.000 --> 08:04.610
some medicine
for bone and tendon injuries.

08:04.610 --> 08:05.830
The effect is very good.

08:05.830 --> 08:07.800
I think in another half month,

08:08.240 --> 08:10.310
even if you can't use swords and spears,

08:10.310 --> 08:12.440
moving freely shouldn't be a problem.

08:25.800 --> 08:26.480
Qiao,

08:27.230 --> 08:29.160
I know you don't believe what I say.

08:29.950 --> 08:32.470
But whether it's Great Yong, Great Yan,

08:32.789 --> 08:33.520
or Biantang,

08:34.360 --> 08:37.240
everyone knows Zhuge Yue died
in battle at Qianzhang Lake.

08:37.240 --> 08:38.360
If he's not dead,

08:39.030 --> 08:40.750
why won't he come to see you?

08:45.720 --> 08:46.360
I think,

08:47.190 --> 08:49.200
after you finish
your last day of medicine,

08:49.200 --> 08:51.130
just come back to Biantang with me.

08:51.410 --> 08:52.740
I'm not going anywhere.

08:53.150 --> 08:54.350
I'll stay right here.

08:55.000 --> 08:55.720
Qiao,

08:56.550 --> 08:58.480
your eyes need 14 days to recover.

08:58.720 --> 09:00.320
The situation in Great Yan
is unstable right now.

09:00.320 --> 09:02.200
It's safest for you to go back
to Biantang with me.

09:02.200 --> 09:04.150
If Great Yan shuts down
due to internal strife,

09:04.150 --> 09:04.870
then

09:04.870 --> 09:07.200
we won't be able to leave
even if we want to.

09:07.840 --> 09:08.510
Li Ce,

09:09.150 --> 09:10.750
I appreciate your kindness.

09:11.270 --> 09:12.530
When my arms get better

09:12.670 --> 09:13.870
and I can move freely,

09:14.240 --> 09:15.360
it'll be fine

09:15.440 --> 09:16.840
for me to stay here alone.

09:17.320 --> 09:18.080
Qiao.

09:18.800 --> 09:19.490
Li Ce,

09:20.510 --> 09:21.300
thank you.

09:23.210 --> 09:25.540
But you don't need to persuade me anymore.

09:34.910 --> 09:35.770
Your Highness,

09:35.790 --> 09:37.360
the situation in Great Yan
is unstable right now.

09:37.360 --> 09:38.670
Cheng Yuan is killing people everywhere.

09:38.670 --> 09:39.670
The various tribes in Great Yan

09:39.670 --> 09:41.270
could rebel at any time.

09:43.080 --> 09:45.860
I'm afraid it's not suitable
for us to stay here for long.

09:45.860 --> 09:47.720
I know everything you're saying.

09:47.960 --> 09:49.890
But Qiao doesn't want to go with me.

10:02.870 --> 10:03.730
Your Highness,

10:03.870 --> 10:05.240
you're the Crown Prince of Biantang.

10:05.240 --> 10:06.200
This affects Biantang.

10:06.200 --> 10:06.860
Song Cheng.

10:07.550 --> 10:08.950
Go hire a few more people.

10:09.200 --> 10:10.460
They need to be strong.

10:10.720 --> 10:12.320
And ropes and wooden sticks.

10:12.910 --> 10:14.170
And knockout incense.

10:14.720 --> 10:15.410
Knockout incense?

10:15.410 --> 10:17.400
Get the carriage
and luggage ready as well.

10:17.400 --> 10:18.460
Tomorrow morning,

10:18.540 --> 10:20.870
after Qiao finishes
her 7th bottle of Huotu water,

10:20.870 --> 10:22.930
we'll take her back to Biantang by force.

10:22.930 --> 10:24.440
She still can't see clearly now,

10:24.440 --> 10:25.670
and her limbs haven't recovered yet.

10:25.670 --> 10:26.870
We'll knock her out

10:27.390 --> 10:28.850
and tie her up if we have to.

10:29.630 --> 10:30.430
Knock her out?

10:30.670 --> 10:31.880
That's General Chu.

10:32.240 --> 10:32.960
Are we able

10:33.630 --> 10:34.720
to beat her?

10:36.510 --> 10:37.310
You're right.

10:38.550 --> 10:39.350
No, no.

10:40.150 --> 10:41.270
That's Qiao.

10:42.910 --> 10:43.710
How about this?

10:43.710 --> 10:45.150
Change ropes to silk.

10:45.510 --> 10:47.440
And buy the best knockout incense.

10:47.690 --> 10:48.810
If that doesn't work,

10:48.810 --> 10:50.500
just mix it in my favorite ambergris.

10:50.500 --> 10:51.360
It smells good.

10:51.540 --> 10:54.190
Prepare the biggest carriage too.

10:54.600 --> 10:56.840
Let's tie her up properly.

10:58.760 --> 11:00.410
What are you waiting for? Go!

11:00.630 --> 11:01.560
Yes, yes.

11:04.240 --> 11:04.750
Right.

11:05.550 --> 11:07.200
Remember to buy Qiao's favorite snacks.

11:07.200 --> 11:08.550
Don't let her starve on the way.

11:08.550 --> 11:09.070
Yes.

11:09.200 --> 11:10.420
I'll go arrange it right away.

11:10.420 --> 11:12.570
I will buy Qiao's favorite

11:13.070 --> 11:13.620
snacks.

11:13.640 --> 11:14.120
You...

11:31.760 --> 11:32.760
I'll do it myself.

11:33.720 --> 11:34.580
Heir Apparent,

11:34.790 --> 11:37.270
Fourth Young Master Zhuge
sent some medicine.

11:37.270 --> 11:39.550
He said when Miss Chu
lived in Qingshan Manor,

11:37.870 --> 11:39.780
♪ On the water ♪

11:39.570 --> 11:40.690
she always used it.

11:39.800 --> 11:41.510
♪ Countless ♪

11:40.970 --> 11:41.810
Zhuge Yue?

11:41.540 --> 11:43.220
♪ Ripples rise ♪

11:42.750 --> 11:43.670
Is he here?

11:44.240 --> 11:46.000
The Fourth Young Master
sent Yue Qi to deliver it.

11:45.510 --> 11:47.580
♪ Through the mortal world ♪

11:47.600 --> 11:51.030
♪ With meetings and goodbyes ♪

11:48.390 --> 11:49.850
I don't want his medicine.

11:50.150 --> 11:51.840
He must be trying to poison me.

11:52.940 --> 11:55.270
♪ How unfair fate is ♪

11:55.300 --> 12:00.300
♪ It gave all the memories back to you ♪

12:00.620 --> 12:02.450
♪ Yet left me ♪

12:01.960 --> 12:03.790
Sending you poison
in this freezing weather?

12:02.480 --> 12:06.060
♪ Stuck right here ♪

12:05.320 --> 12:07.580
You really take yourself too seriously.

12:08.000 --> 12:10.440
Sending medicine to a servant like me
in this freezing weather?

12:08.190 --> 12:09.410
♪ Rain falls down ♪

12:09.760 --> 12:11.160
♪ Lingering thoughts ♪

12:10.790 --> 12:12.200
It must be hard for you

12:11.930 --> 12:14.160
♪ Awake once more ♪

12:12.200 --> 12:13.530
to take so much trouble.

12:15.360 --> 12:16.580
Sharp-tongued.

12:15.650 --> 12:17.830
♪ Let the wind shape ♪

12:17.120 --> 12:19.080
I think you've fully recovered
from your illness.

12:18.070 --> 12:21.720
♪ Another me ♪

12:23.650 --> 12:25.650
♪ How can I escape ♪

12:25.680 --> 12:30.440
♪ All the reflections that hold you? ♪

12:31.060 --> 12:34.040
♪ Behind the illusions
of the moon in water ♪

12:34.950 --> 12:37.660
♪ I wait to sink deep ♪

12:37.690 --> 12:42.110
♪ May fortune smile on all below ♪

12:42.300 --> 12:45.900
♪ Just to hear when you'll come home ♪

12:46.340 --> 12:48.340
♪ Braving schemes alone ♪

12:48.370 --> 12:50.080
♪ Treading through thorns ♪

12:50.110 --> 12:52.710
♪ Searching for your name ♪

12:52.790 --> 12:57.510
♪ Till storms rise again ♪

12:57.540 --> 13:01.420
♪ Not a single regret remains ♪

13:01.440 --> 13:03.440
♪ Melt the ice ♪

13:03.470 --> 13:05.470
♪ That fate has wrought ♪

13:05.490 --> 13:10.700
♪ Let the night ♪

13:12.050 --> 13:17.370
♪ Forever glow ♪

13:36.340 --> 13:37.100
Who are you?

13:41.360 --> 13:42.490
Who exactly are you?

13:42.700 --> 13:44.500
Why did you bring me Huotu water?

13:59.510 --> 14:00.120
Qi.

14:00.910 --> 14:02.200
Are you Yue Qi?

14:02.840 --> 14:04.960
Yue Qi, why won't you speak?

14:12.910 --> 14:14.070
Did you become mute

14:15.480 --> 14:17.610
from your injuries at the frozen lake?

14:19.670 --> 14:20.870
What about Zhuge Yue?

14:21.240 --> 14:22.320
Where is Zhuge Yue?

14:50.440 --> 14:51.270
Impossible.

14:52.440 --> 14:53.270
Impossible.

14:54.960 --> 14:56.020
You're lying to me.

14:57.000 --> 14:58.030
He's not dead.

14:58.910 --> 15:01.170
He clearly saved me from the frozen lake.

15:01.190 --> 15:03.320
Why didn't the Moon Guard look for him?

15:03.750 --> 15:05.280
Why didn't you look for him?

15:05.320 --> 15:06.410
Go find him!

15:06.430 --> 15:07.550
Find him!

15:07.820 --> 15:09.750
Find him! Find him!

16:20.880 --> 16:24.500
♪ The dust in the world ♪

16:24.930 --> 16:28.400
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

16:27.550 --> 16:28.600
You are Zhuge Yue,

16:29.110 --> 16:31.910
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

16:29.600 --> 16:30.600
not Yue Qi.

16:32.740 --> 16:34.090
♪ And not be scared? ♪

16:34.120 --> 16:36.130
♪ A slight ripple ♪

16:36.310 --> 16:39.910
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

16:37.720 --> 16:39.200
This was left behind

16:39.790 --> 16:40.790
when you saved me,

16:40.190 --> 16:43.560
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

16:41.360 --> 16:42.240
right?

16:44.530 --> 16:47.370
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

16:48.030 --> 16:51.410
♪ Let it be ♪

16:48.870 --> 16:54.080
I am Yue Qi.

16:52.490 --> 16:55.920
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

16:54.630 --> 16:55.790
Zhuge Yue

16:56.390 --> 16:59.410
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

16:58.440 --> 16:59.360
is dead.

16:59.780 --> 17:01.420
♪ Go weaving ♪

17:01.740 --> 17:06.700
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

17:07.210 --> 17:10.010
♪ We once beheld ♪

17:10.030 --> 17:13.440
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

17:15.160 --> 17:17.800
♪ Beauty never ♪

17:17.819 --> 17:22.560
♪ Lasts for long ♪

17:22.819 --> 17:26.349
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

17:26.369 --> 17:30.810
♪ It's just a stone ♪

17:31.100 --> 17:38.310
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

17:38.990 --> 17:49.770
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

17:50.720 --> 17:53.110
Zhuge Yue has a scar on his left hand.

17:53.800 --> 17:55.160
It is crescent-shaped.

18:19.880 --> 18:21.030
You are not him.

18:22.440 --> 18:24.000
You are not Zhuge Yue.

19:09.780 --> 19:12.540
The medicine I gave you is a 10-day dose.

19:12.570 --> 19:15.140
It's enough for you to go back
and save your woman.

19:15.140 --> 19:17.860
If you don't return
as promised in 10 days,

19:17.890 --> 19:19.540
I'll let you know

19:19.560 --> 19:22.430
what a living hell is.

19:33.240 --> 19:34.790
Once you take it,

19:34.790 --> 19:37.350
the scar on your body will heal.

19:37.590 --> 19:41.000
All traces of who you used to be
will be erased.

19:41.000 --> 19:44.160
From now on, Zhuge Yue will no longer
exist in this world.

19:44.440 --> 19:46.750
You will only be my shadow,

19:47.030 --> 19:48.880
my slave.

20:14.880 --> 20:15.680
Your Highness,

20:15.680 --> 20:17.310
you must make a decision quickly.

20:17.310 --> 20:18.200
The Black Eagle Army of Great Yan

20:18.200 --> 20:19.880
is searching this area right now.

20:19.880 --> 20:21.610
If you don't take Miss Chu away,

20:21.960 --> 20:25.270
we won't be able to retreat unscathed.

20:30.510 --> 20:31.370
How about this?

20:31.510 --> 20:35.640
I will count to 3,

20:35.960 --> 20:37.420
and we charge in together.

20:37.440 --> 20:38.310
Understand?

20:38.720 --> 20:39.450
Understood.

20:43.350 --> 20:43.720
One.

20:44.440 --> 20:45.310
Two.

20:45.960 --> 20:46.510
Three.

20:47.030 --> 20:47.890
Your Highness.

20:48.030 --> 20:50.200
Are you sure Miss Chu's martial arts

20:50.880 --> 20:52.140
haven't returned yet?

20:52.160 --> 20:53.010
Not sure.

20:53.750 --> 20:54.110
But

20:54.590 --> 20:55.400
I'm sure,

20:55.570 --> 20:57.960
certain, and positive

20:58.510 --> 21:00.370
that her eyes haven't recovered.

21:01.160 --> 21:02.120
Let's play it by ear.

21:02.120 --> 21:03.850
-Play it by ear.
-Play it by ear.

21:07.510 --> 21:08.070
One.

21:09.830 --> 21:10.400
Two.

21:11.790 --> 21:12.350
Three.

21:24.400 --> 21:25.030
Qiao.

21:32.030 --> 21:33.030
Whose is this?

21:36.790 --> 21:37.350
Qiao.

21:37.790 --> 21:39.200
I... I...

21:39.200 --> 21:39.790
Li Ce,

21:40.200 --> 21:42.060
I'll go back to Biantang with you.

21:52.670 --> 21:53.530
Your Highness,

21:53.600 --> 21:54.510
right now, inside the city of Great Yan,

21:54.510 --> 21:56.160
people are searching
for Miss Chu everywhere.

21:56.160 --> 21:57.310
Why are the borders of Great Yan

21:57.310 --> 21:58.790
guarded so poorly?

21:58.960 --> 22:01.750
Could there be some changes
in the city of Great Yan?

22:01.750 --> 22:02.720
Hurry out of the city.

22:02.720 --> 22:03.510
Don't stop.

22:03.880 --> 22:04.470
Yes.

22:08.130 --> 22:10.920
[Itinerant Court, Great Yan]

22:17.680 --> 22:19.110
His Majesty is unconscious.

22:19.110 --> 22:20.000
Cheng Yuan blocked the news,

22:20.000 --> 22:21.510
and we can't find out anything!

22:21.510 --> 22:23.350
Could it be that the worst has happened?

22:21.840 --> 22:23.440
[Huo Sang,
Elder of the Baichuan Tribe of Great Yan]

22:23.550 --> 22:25.000
The worst has happened?

22:23.650 --> 22:24.760
[Tu Bo,
Elder of the Hongchuan Tribe of Great Yan]

22:25.460 --> 22:28.180
I'm afraid he won't wake up.

22:29.590 --> 22:31.420
Elders, don't be too anxious.

22:32.150 --> 22:34.080
Let's wait for news of His Majesty.

22:34.350 --> 22:37.190
If His Majesty really doesn't wake up,

22:35.730 --> 22:37.220
[Katuo,
Chief of the Jinhui Tribe of Great Yan]

22:37.830 --> 22:40.350
there is someone
who can take over his position.

22:40.350 --> 22:41.160
You mean...

22:41.700 --> 22:43.000
[Elder of the Lanchuan Tribe of Great Yan]

22:42.270 --> 22:43.400
the Snowy Region Tribe?

22:43.400 --> 22:44.530
In terms of kinship,

22:44.680 --> 22:47.110
General Huan
is His Majesty's cousin after all.

22:47.110 --> 22:49.560
The Yan family all died
at the hands of the Yong people,

22:49.560 --> 22:51.020
leaving only His Majesty.

22:51.030 --> 22:52.790
His Majesty is not married yet.

22:52.930 --> 22:54.300
If something happens,

22:54.470 --> 22:57.100
Huan Huan taking over the position
of King of Great Yan

22:57.100 --> 22:58.900
would be perfectly reasonable.

23:04.310 --> 23:05.790
How can

23:06.750 --> 23:08.610
a little girl inherit the throne?

23:08.750 --> 23:10.110
But this little girl

23:10.680 --> 23:12.140
has made more military achievements

23:12.140 --> 23:13.940
than all of us combined.

23:15.160 --> 23:17.960
Plus, with the prestige
of the Snowy Region Tribe,

23:18.240 --> 23:19.650
I'm afraid that when the time comes,

23:19.650 --> 23:21.610
even Hongchuan and Pale,

23:22.350 --> 23:24.270
tribes with deep foundations,

23:24.850 --> 23:26.250
can hardly turn the tide.

23:28.520 --> 23:30.380
Chief of the Jinhui Tribe's words

23:30.960 --> 23:32.430
are indeed reasonable.

23:33.830 --> 23:35.550
In terms of military achievements,

23:35.550 --> 23:37.810
we are far behind the Snowy Region Tribe.

23:40.260 --> 23:41.550
But Chief of the Jinhui Tribe,

23:41.550 --> 23:43.160
you are also a young hero.

23:43.790 --> 23:45.440
Why let your own tribe

23:46.430 --> 23:48.800
be subordinate to others?

23:52.150 --> 23:54.240
Elder Pale, you truly understand me.

23:59.070 --> 24:01.270
Naturally, I won't let Jinhui

24:02.720 --> 24:04.920
be subordinate to anyone else.

24:10.240 --> 24:11.200
Lady Helian.

24:17.160 --> 24:18.680
I have brought someone

24:19.440 --> 24:20.960
to you, General Cheng.

24:52.230 --> 24:53.830
[Wunan Goddess]

25:53.110 --> 25:54.110
Can your medicine

25:54.410 --> 25:56.400
really cure His Majesty's illness?

25:56.400 --> 25:58.030
When will His Majesty wake up?

25:58.030 --> 26:01.690
This medicine is definitely effective.
Please trust me, My Lord.

26:04.410 --> 26:05.500
I am also confused

26:06.830 --> 26:08.400
about your doubts.

26:09.230 --> 26:10.990
Or there's a possibility...

26:13.440 --> 26:16.110
that His Majesty is the true ruler

26:16.440 --> 26:18.240
blessed by the gods of Great Yan.

26:21.870 --> 26:23.730
If you want His Majesty to wake up,

26:24.030 --> 26:26.840
my medicine alone is not enough.

26:27.960 --> 26:29.330
It also needs...

26:32.880 --> 26:35.440
the will of the gods.

26:53.300 --> 26:54.580
Men of our tribe,

26:55.590 --> 26:57.790
for hundreds of years, our Jinhui Tribe

26:58.510 --> 27:01.030
has always been the cheetahs
of the grasslands.

27:01.030 --> 27:01.880
Warriors,

27:02.440 --> 27:03.350
tell me,

27:03.710 --> 27:05.080
what is a cheetah?

27:06.590 --> 27:07.440
The king!

27:07.590 --> 27:09.100
The king of the grasslands!

27:09.100 --> 27:09.970
For centuries,

27:10.870 --> 27:13.350
we've pledged our loyalty
to the Black Eagles of the grasslands

27:13.350 --> 27:14.790
and served the Yan family as kings.

27:14.790 --> 27:16.440
But what did the Yan family do?

27:16.440 --> 27:18.310
What have they brought to the grasslands?

27:18.310 --> 27:19.240
Yan Shicheng

27:19.720 --> 27:21.350
let his emotions dictate his actions,

27:21.350 --> 27:23.880
ruining the lives
of over a dozen of his own kin

27:24.070 --> 27:26.310
and plunging Great Yan into peril.

27:26.830 --> 27:28.160
And Yan Xun,

27:28.510 --> 27:30.080
for his own selfish desires,

27:30.080 --> 27:32.150
ambushed the Yong Army at Mount Ximin,

27:32.150 --> 27:36.590
leaving tens of thousands of Yan Army
soldiers dead at Meilin Pass.

27:37.400 --> 27:40.070
And for a Yong woman,

27:40.310 --> 27:43.510
he disregarded the safety of Great Yan.

27:44.590 --> 27:45.990
How can such a Black Eagle

27:46.310 --> 27:48.030
be King?

27:48.030 --> 27:52.160
-Not fit to be King! Not fit to be King!
-Not fit to be King! Not fit to be King!

27:53.020 --> 27:54.010
Warriors!

27:55.240 --> 27:56.240
Follow me

27:56.720 --> 27:58.000
to capture Great Yan

27:58.640 --> 28:00.720
and kill Yan Xun!

28:00.720 --> 28:03.790
-Capture Great Yan! Kill Yan Xun!
-Capture Great Yan! Kill Yan Xun!

28:03.790 --> 28:07.070
-Capture Great Yan! Kill Yan Xun!
-Capture Great Yan! Kill Yan Xun!

28:07.070 --> 28:10.800
-Capture Great Yan! Kill Yan Xun!
-Capture Great Yan! Kill Yan Xun!

28:14.960 --> 28:16.550
Urgent report!

28:25.960 --> 28:26.480
Here.

28:32.070 --> 28:32.870
General Huan.

28:33.510 --> 28:35.680
Katuo has rebelled
with 30,000 Jinhui soldiers.

28:35.680 --> 28:37.940
They're approaching the Great Yan camp!

28:38.160 --> 28:39.270
Of the 13 tribes of Great Yan,

28:39.270 --> 28:41.240
7 have already started
mobilizing their troops.

28:41.240 --> 28:41.830
What?

28:42.350 --> 28:43.470
Katuo has rebelled?

28:43.470 --> 28:44.070
Huan,

28:44.550 --> 28:45.350
you can't get involved.

28:45.350 --> 28:46.640
Together with General Cheng,

28:46.640 --> 28:47.920
we only have 10,000 Black Eagle soldiers,

28:47.920 --> 28:49.720
who are responsible
for guarding the Capital of Great Yan.

28:49.720 --> 28:50.960
Unless they attack the capital,

28:50.480 --> 28:51.570
[An Luo, Snowy Region Tribe of Great Yan]

28:50.960 --> 28:52.090
we can't intervene.

28:53.240 --> 28:54.040
General Huan!

28:54.350 --> 28:56.750
The rebels are only 20 li
from the Great Yan camp.

28:56.750 --> 28:58.160
They will arrive soon!

28:58.590 --> 29:00.790
Please give your orders, General Huan.

29:07.550 --> 29:09.160
I will ask General Shiyan for help.

29:09.160 --> 29:10.440
We are kin of the Yan family.

29:10.440 --> 29:11.550
I'll use the loyalty
of my Snowy Region Tribe

29:11.550 --> 29:13.070
and our prestige in Great Yan

29:13.070 --> 29:14.680
to take charge of the military
on behalf of His Majesty.

29:14.680 --> 29:15.270
Huan,

29:15.550 --> 29:16.850
you're going to command the whole army?

29:16.850 --> 29:17.440
Yes.

29:19.640 --> 29:20.550
If I don't,

29:21.350 --> 29:24.080
Great Yan will immediately
fall into a civil war.

29:27.440 --> 29:28.570
They're attacking.

29:35.270 --> 29:36.400
Soldiers!

29:36.960 --> 29:38.560
You are the Black Eagle Army,

29:38.590 --> 29:39.720
the Great Yan Army,

29:39.960 --> 29:42.590
the strongest warriors
defending Great Yan!

29:43.350 --> 29:45.590
Now someone is rebelling

29:46.070 --> 29:48.120
and trying to destroy
the unity of Great Yan.

29:48.120 --> 29:49.430
What should we do?

29:49.750 --> 29:51.400
Defend Great Yan to the death!

29:51.400 --> 29:53.510
-Defend Great Yan to the death!
-Defend Great Yan to the death!

29:53.510 --> 29:55.240
-Defend Great Yan to the death!
-Defend Great Yan to the death!

29:55.240 --> 29:56.550
From now on,

29:57.110 --> 30:00.440
I'll take charge of the entire army
on behalf of King Yan Xun!

30:00.790 --> 30:01.680
Soldiers,

30:02.160 --> 30:03.830
follow me to fight the rebels

30:04.070 --> 30:05.440
and defend Great Yan!

30:05.750 --> 30:08.890
-Fight the rebels! Defend Great Yan!
-Fight the rebels! Defend Great Yan!

30:08.890 --> 30:12.220
-Fight the rebels! Defend Great Yan!
-Fight the rebels! Defend Great Yan!

30:12.220 --> 30:15.150
-Defend Great Yan!
-Defend Great Yan!

30:15.180 --> 30:19.310
-Fight the rebels! Defend Great Yan!
-Fight the rebels! Defend Great Yan!

30:22.620 --> 30:25.850
[Border of Biantang, Great Yong]

30:28.030 --> 30:28.560
Chun'er.

30:28.960 --> 30:30.760
The situation is turbulent now,

30:31.110 --> 30:32.960
and I don't know what will happen.

30:32.960 --> 30:34.690
I must focus on dealing with it.

30:35.880 --> 30:37.810
So I can't keep you here any longer.

30:39.680 --> 30:40.640
This guard

30:41.400 --> 30:43.310
will escort you back to Great Yong.

30:43.310 --> 30:44.770
Take good care of yourself

30:45.920 --> 30:47.780
and don't cause any more trouble.

30:47.880 --> 30:48.640
Che.

30:51.510 --> 30:53.030
This lake is so blue

30:54.110 --> 30:55.270
and so clean.

30:56.350 --> 30:57.670
Do you still remember?

30:58.000 --> 31:00.160
When we were in Zhenhuang City,

31:01.270 --> 31:02.930
every Double Third Festival,

31:03.300 --> 31:05.430
we would go for a picnic in the suburbs.

31:05.940 --> 31:08.600
The Luo River
that flows through Zhenhuang City

31:08.920 --> 31:10.160
is also so clear

31:11.000 --> 31:11.880
and blue.

31:16.680 --> 31:17.270
Chun'er,

31:17.830 --> 31:18.680
let's go.

31:32.150 --> 31:32.790
Chun'er!

31:33.030 --> 31:33.680
Save her!

31:33.830 --> 31:34.790
Save her!

32:03.390 --> 32:05.160
[Tomb of Li Ru, Prince of Chang]

32:07.280 --> 32:11.890
[Li Yan, Prince of Luo, Biantang]

32:12.240 --> 32:13.100
Your Highness!

32:13.880 --> 32:14.740
Your Highness!

32:15.720 --> 32:16.580
Your Highness!

32:17.440 --> 32:19.040
Someone fell into the water!

32:47.070 --> 32:47.680
Qiao.

32:48.510 --> 32:51.030
It's been a few days
since you finished the Huotu water.

32:51.030 --> 32:52.510
Are your eyes feeling any better?

32:52.510 --> 32:53.710
Can you see anything?

32:54.200 --> 32:54.880
Like,

32:55.590 --> 32:57.240
my handsome figure.

33:07.590 --> 33:08.110
Right.

33:08.480 --> 33:09.680
You are blindfolded,

33:09.830 --> 33:11.400
so you shouldn't be able to see anything.

33:11.400 --> 33:12.060
Never mind.

33:12.480 --> 33:14.340
I'll just wait until the 14th day.

33:18.480 --> 33:19.110
Qiao,

33:19.240 --> 33:20.350
I specifically asked Song Cheng

33:20.350 --> 33:21.400
to buy you

33:21.460 --> 33:23.260
these delicious snacks in town.

33:23.350 --> 33:24.790
Great Yan is a poor place.

33:25.110 --> 33:27.420
The food and drinks
are not as good as Biantang's.

33:27.420 --> 33:29.220
You must be hungry. Have a taste.

33:47.400 --> 33:48.070
Qiao,

33:48.350 --> 33:49.680
we've arrived at a town.

33:49.750 --> 33:50.560
There's a lantern show.

33:50.560 --> 33:51.690
Let's go take a look.

33:52.480 --> 33:53.200
No need.

33:57.540 --> 33:58.170
Qiao,

33:58.480 --> 33:59.440
don't be sad.

34:00.070 --> 34:01.160
If you ask me,

34:01.880 --> 34:03.480
Zhuge Yue might not be dead.

34:03.720 --> 34:04.510
Think about it.

34:04.510 --> 34:07.480
He's highly skilled in martial arts
and very cunning.

34:07.480 --> 34:08.800
He's always killing others.

34:08.800 --> 34:09.920
How could he die?

34:10.440 --> 34:11.150
No way.

34:11.380 --> 34:12.460
He must be alive.

34:16.800 --> 34:17.320
Really.

34:17.670 --> 34:18.670
Is it possible

34:19.070 --> 34:21.130
that he was saved by a foreign weirdo,

34:21.480 --> 34:22.920
and under that weirdo's pressure,

34:22.920 --> 34:24.070
he doesn't dare to acknowledge you,

34:24.070 --> 34:25.280
afraid of bringing you danger,

34:25.280 --> 34:26.880
so he's been hiding from you?

34:27.320 --> 34:28.150
You know,

34:28.440 --> 34:29.440
foreigners

34:29.590 --> 34:31.449
must have some weird fetishes...

34:33.400 --> 34:34.190
What's wrong?

34:34.190 --> 34:37.050
Get off the carriage.
Let's watch the lantern show.

34:43.710 --> 34:44.270
Let's go.

34:46.960 --> 34:47.590
Careful.

34:48.409 --> 34:48.850
Come.

34:52.960 --> 34:53.670
Qiao,

34:53.920 --> 34:54.800
this is the lantern show.

34:54.800 --> 34:55.800
It's very lively.

34:57.910 --> 34:59.370
They sell lanterns ahead.

34:59.380 --> 35:00.980
Let me take you to have a look.

35:14.710 --> 35:15.590
Watch your step.

35:15.590 --> 35:16.320
Lanterns.

35:15.960 --> 35:17.870
♪ Through the mortal world ♪

35:17.510 --> 35:18.230
Lanterns.

35:17.980 --> 35:21.050
♪ With meetings and goodbyes ♪

35:19.320 --> 35:19.920
Sir and Madam,

35:19.920 --> 35:21.230
take a look at my lanterns.

35:21.230 --> 35:23.210
We're here. They sell lanterns here.

35:23.210 --> 35:25.620
♪ How unfair fate is ♪

35:24.320 --> 35:25.030
Sir,

35:25.650 --> 35:30.300
♪ It gave all the memories back to you ♪

35:26.440 --> 35:28.040
do you have rabbit lanterns?

35:30.910 --> 35:32.540
♪ Yet left me ♪

35:31.800 --> 35:33.510
The more you care about
worldly possessions,

35:33.090 --> 35:36.000
♪ Stuck right here ♪

35:34.030 --> 35:36.230
the more they will hinder your actions.

35:37.190 --> 35:38.550
If a person has no attachments,

35:38.370 --> 35:40.040
♪ Rain falls down ♪

35:39.110 --> 35:40.800
what is the point
of being like a block of wood?

35:40.330 --> 35:41.800
♪ Lingering thoughts ♪

35:41.110 --> 35:42.440
If one day,

35:42.260 --> 35:44.800
♪ Awake once more ♪

35:42.590 --> 35:44.450
the enemy uses what you care about

35:44.840 --> 35:46.480
to confuse your mind and take your life,

35:46.280 --> 35:48.290
♪ Let the wind shape ♪

35:46.840 --> 35:48.630
and you implicate others when you die,

35:48.360 --> 35:52.800
♪ Another me ♪

35:48.840 --> 35:50.070
then you will know

35:50.320 --> 35:52.720
whether being a block of wood
is good or bad.

35:53.970 --> 35:55.970
♪ How can I escape ♪

35:55.990 --> 36:00.750
♪ All the reflections that hold you? ♪

36:01.490 --> 36:04.130
♪ Behind the illusions
of the moon in water ♪

36:05.300 --> 36:08.040
♪ I wait to sink deep ♪

36:08.060 --> 36:12.510
♪ May fortune smile on all below ♪

36:12.690 --> 36:16.140
♪ Just to hear when you'll come home ♪

36:14.440 --> 36:15.400
Didn't you say

36:15.880 --> 36:18.280
that having attachments
would hinder your actions?

36:16.830 --> 36:18.640
♪ Braving schemes alone ♪

36:18.510 --> 36:19.510
It's just a lantern.

36:18.670 --> 36:20.360
♪ Treading through thorns ♪

36:20.380 --> 36:23.190
♪ Searching for your name ♪

36:20.400 --> 36:22.130
You know so little of the world.

36:22.510 --> 36:24.150
You would just keep thinking about it
if I hadn't bought it for you.

36:23.220 --> 36:27.650
♪ Till storms rise again ♪

36:28.010 --> 36:31.550
♪ Not a single regret remains ♪

36:31.860 --> 36:33.860
♪ Melt the ice ♪

36:33.880 --> 36:35.880
♪ That fate has wrought ♪

36:36.000 --> 36:39.440
♪ Let the night ♪

36:41.800 --> 36:48.260
♪ Forever glow ♪

37:08.010 --> 37:11.540
[Tangjing, Biantang]

37:10.760 --> 37:11.480
Let me see.

37:12.150 --> 37:12.630
Stop!

37:12.630 --> 37:13.230
Go ahead.

37:14.960 --> 37:16.220
Who is in the carriage?

37:17.840 --> 37:18.510
Why?

37:19.070 --> 37:21.000
You want to search my carriage too?

37:21.510 --> 37:23.590
Your Highness, I pay my respects to you.

37:23.590 --> 37:24.710
Great Yan has been in turmoil recently.

37:24.710 --> 37:25.920
To prevent it from affecting Biantang,

37:25.920 --> 37:26.800
our superiors ordered

37:26.800 --> 37:28.760
that all personnel entering the city
must be strictly searched.

37:28.760 --> 37:30.280
Since it is your duty,

37:30.630 --> 37:31.670
I won't blame you.

37:32.360 --> 37:33.030
Well,

37:33.250 --> 37:34.560
I have an exotic beauty in my carriage

37:34.560 --> 37:36.230
that I brought back from my travels.

37:36.230 --> 37:38.070
Why don't you get in and check

37:38.760 --> 37:40.960
if she is a spy from Great Yan?

37:41.360 --> 37:42.190
I wouldn't dare.

37:42.190 --> 37:44.320
Please enter the city, Your Highness.

37:51.490 --> 37:52.570
Chu Qiao?

38:22.070 --> 38:23.400
We have lost our way.

38:24.190 --> 38:25.120
If we keep going,

38:25.400 --> 38:27.150
none of us will make it back alive.

38:27.150 --> 38:27.960
Who are you?

38:28.000 --> 38:28.840
What do you want?

38:28.840 --> 38:29.670
Zhuge Yue!

38:29.800 --> 38:31.440
Your Majesty, you mean

38:31.440 --> 38:33.880
that the woman's identity is suspicious.

38:34.310 --> 38:35.920
You've been with me for 3 days.

38:35.920 --> 38:38.070
Why don't you ask who I am?

38:39.320 --> 38:39.920
Zhuge Yue.

38:40.960 --> 38:42.030
I saw you.
